A simple visualization of matrix composition in game code:

```cpp
// Concept of matrix composition in engine coding
struct FMatrix {
    float M[4][4];
    static FMatrix Identity();
    FMatrix operator*(const FMatrix& Other) const;
};

FMatrix GetWorldTransform(FMatrix ScaleMatrix, FMatrix RotationMatrix, FMatrix TranslationMatrix) {
    // TRS composition order (Unreal/DirectX right-to-left or left-to-right depending on conventions)
    // Here we perform Scale * Rotation * Translation
    FMatrix Result = ScaleMatrix * RotationMatrix * TranslationMatrix;
    return Result;
}
```
